  "text": "In recent years, oral, injectable, transdermal, or other forms of drugs are available as the means to conduct ART [CITATION_1] . In Japan, however, transdermal patches or gels of testosterone are still not available for ART, and to date intramuscular (IM)-ART is the only approved treatment for hypogonadism. Therefore, more data is needed on endocrine kinetics after IM-ART.",
